### List All Evaluations
GET {{baseUrl}}/ivcf-evaluations/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List Evaluations with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/ivcf-evaluations/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}?skip=0&limit=3

### Filter Evaluations by Patient
GET {{baseUrl}}/ivcf-evaluations/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}?patient_id=1

### Filter Evaluations by Period
GET {{baseUrl}}/ivcf-evaluations/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}?period_from=2024-01-01&period_to=2024-01-31

### Filter Evaluations by Classification
GET {{baseUrl}}/ivcf-evaluations/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}?classificacao=Frágil

### Filter Evaluations by Classification (Robusto)
GET {{baseUrl}}/ivcf-evaluations/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}?classificacao=Robusto

### Filter Evaluations by Classification (Em Risco)
GET {{baseUrl}}/ivcf-evaluations/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}?classificacao=Em Risco

### Get Evaluation by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/ivcf-evaluations/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}1

### Get Critical Patients
GET {{baseUrl}}/ivcf-evaluations/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}critical-patients

### Get Critical Patients with Higher Threshold
GET {{baseUrl}}/ivcf-evaluations/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}critical-patients?pontuacao_minima=30

